start.label: enemy of your enemy is your friend

examples.en: The tank was hit by enemy fire.
The enemy showed no mercy.
Our troops attacked the enemy.
The enemy was in full flight.
Boredom is the enemy of learning.
Enemy forces have taken the airport.
They prostrated the enemy.
She's a dangerous enemy to have.
They regarded him as their enemy.
examples.ru: Они видели в нём своего врага.

examples.en: Did you get down the enemy plane?
Tradition is the enemy of progress.
The enemy pillaged the town.
The enemy exploded the bridge.
The enemy launched an invasion.
A pawn takes the enemy angularly.
examples.ru: Пешка бьёт фигуру противника по диагонали.

examples.en: Moonlight is the smuggler's enemy.
The enemy is closing in on the city.
He outbraved the enemy.
examples.ru: Он не побоялся врага. / Он храбро сопротивлялся противнику.

examples.en: They shelled the enemy troops.
The army outflanked the enemy.
They attacked the enemy's line.
The enemy had mined the harbor.
The soldiers fired on the enemy.
Enemy forces assaulted the city.
The enemy attacked treacherously.
The enemy troops were annihilated.
He was shot down by enemy fighters.
We pushed deep into enemy territory.
The enemy has suffered heavy losses.
I finally settled with my old enemy.
examples.ru: Я наконец-то расквитался со своим старым врагом.
